Bank of Israel Suggests Designating Land for Rental Construction

-- B y   A l i s a   O d e n h e i m e r
-- 
2011-10-02T11:05:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-02/bank-of-israel-suggests-designating-land-for-rental-construction.html
The Bank of  Israel  recommends
designating some land in urban construction programs for
building rental housing in order to help increase their supply,
according to an e-mailed report. The central bank also said
rental subsidies have eroded and recommended updating them.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alisa Odenheimer in Jerusalem at 
 aodenheimer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Calev Ben-David at 
 cbendavid@bloomberg.net  